reviewText: I bought it because I was an extra in the movie an incident at Calais. However I found all of the short films entertaining!
I enjoyed this very much, and I got it right away and I am glad for that. Thank You for making that happen. I enjoy dvds and look forward to getting more from amazon.

This was one of the first DVDs I bought and it blew me away . I found all the shorts entertaining, but Bingo really stood out . The whole disk is really cool from it's navigation to its content. Check it out!
